00:27:23.700 --> 00:27:29.779
provided answers to the very questions that he had been asking? As he learned more from the Bible,

00:27:29.779 --> 00:27:36.420
Jose made changes in his way of life and in his thinking. He learned to imitate God's love

00:27:36.420 --> 00:27:42.740
and thereby become his friend. Breaking his ties with his companions, though, proved to be challenging.

00:27:43.380 --> 00:27:47.619
Every time you went to the kingdom hall of Jehovah's Witnesses, he was followed.

00:27:48.579 --> 00:27:53.700
Some former associates even attended a few meetings, so asked to understand what brought about

00:27:53.700 --> 00:27:59.940
such a great change in Jose. But once they were satisfied that he was not a danger to them,

00:27:59.940 --> 00:28:07.940
they left him alone. At age 17, Jose was baptized as one of Jehovah's Witnesses. As God's friend,

00:28:08.500 --> 00:28:14.420
Jose soon started sharing what he was learning full-time. Instead of scheming to kill people,

00:28:15.140 --> 00:28:22.339
he could now share a message of love and of hope with them. What a great reward for choosing to

00:28:22.339 --> 00:28:29.059
become Jehovah's Friend. Yes, even those who were once enemies can learn to be at peace with one

00:28:29.059 --> 00:28:37.140
another and be God's friends. So what have we learned? We have reviewed why friendship with God

00:28:37.140 --> 00:28:44.980
is realistic and possible for us. The Bible tells us that since ancient times, God has called some

00:28:44.980 --> 00:28:52.099
humans his friends. We also looked at what God has done to heal the breach or close the gap between

00:28:52.099 --> 00:29:00.819
us and him. How has he done so? By means of his Son. Through Jesus, Jehovah God provided the

00:29:00.900 --> 00:29:07.700
ransom sacrifice that was needed to redeem us from sin. Then we looked at what you must do to take

00:29:07.700 --> 00:29:14.900
advantage of God's mercy and become his friend. This includes studying his word the Bible and then

00:29:14.900 --> 00:29:22.660
imitating his outstanding qualities. Finally, we considered how you can find a meaningful life now

00:29:23.380 --> 00:29:30.740
as well as true peace with others. Jehovah promises that his friends will receive

00:29:30.740 --> 00:29:40.180
eternal life in peace. If that is what you yearn for, then please accept our invitation to study

00:29:40.180 --> 00:29:47.619
the Bible with Jehovah's Witnesses. By doing so, you will learn about an unending future when

00:29:47.700 --> 00:29:55.140
anguish of heart is gone forever and an unending future in which God will permanently wipe away

00:29:55.140 --> 00:30:04.660
tears from the faces of his friends. That future is not only possible, it is the future that God

00:30:04.660 --> 00:30:12.779
promises. Thank you, Brother Cook, for helping us to see how friendship with God leads to

00:30:12.779 --> 00:30:20.569
genuine peace. Around the earth, millions are pursuing peace and building faith in Jehovah God

00:30:20.569 --> 00:30:26.569
and his word the Bible. If you would like to have Bible discussions free of charge at the time

00:30:26.569 --> 00:30:35.289
and place convenient for you, please inform one of Jehovah's Witnesses or visit jw.org and fill out

