an online request for a Bible study. We will be happy to arrange for one of Jehovah's Witnesses

00:30:40.970 --> 00:30:48.009
to assist you. Additionally, you can find interactive self-guided Bible study lessons on our

00:30:48.009 --> 00:30:56.819
website, jw.org. We have reached the conclusion of this session. We look forward to the next session

00:30:56.819 --> 00:31:04.099
in which we will see part two of our future Bible drama, Jehovah guides us in the way of peace.

